'''乐声安峰'''（{{lang-en|Roxy Ann Peak}}）坐落在[[美国|美国]][[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[杰克逊县_(俄勒冈州)|杰克逊县]][[梅德福_(俄勒冈州)|梅德福]]的东部边缘，高1090米，是西喀斯喀特山脉的一部分。山峰拥有多个地质层，大部分都是由[[火山|火山岩]]组成，形成时间可以追溯到[[渐新世|渐新世]]早期。乐声安峰的下山坡主要由[[橡树稀树草原|橡树稀树草原]]和开阔[[草原|草原]]覆盖，到了上山坡和峰顶则混有[[温带针叶林|针叶林]]。虽然山峰的[[地形突起度|相对高度]]较低，只有230米，却比梅德福高了670米，在[[罗格谷|罗格谷]]大部分地点都可以看到。该峰是梅德福最重要的[[视域|视域]]、游憩和休闲所在。

乐声安峰的首批定居者是[[美国原住民|美国境内原住民]]部落[[拉特加瓦人|拉特加瓦人]]（{{lang|en|Latgawa}}）的祖先，他们于8000到10000年前来到这里。19世纪50年代初，大量非[[原住民|原住民]]人口来此定居导致[[罗格河战争|罗格河战争]]爆发。战争结束后，拉特加瓦人被迫离开这一地区前往[[印第安保留地|保留地]]。这座山峰就是在19世纪50年代末以最早的其中一位土地所有者乐声·安·博文命名。

1883年，梅德福市在乐声安峰西面建成，并在两年后[[市法团|注册成立]]。1930至1933年间，该市分别从[[国际狮子会|国际狮子会]]和[[美国联邦政府|美国联邦政府]]获得了大量土地，并于1937年建立了占地704公顷的'''普雷斯科特公园'''。乐声安峰的上层山坡和峰顶的大部分区域都位于这座公园的保护范围，并且很大程度上没有经过人类的开发。山峰的南部山麓有一些快速扩张的[[独户住宅区|独户住宅区]]。

== 地质 ==
乐声安峰属于历史悠久的西喀斯喀特的组成部分，这些部分受到了深层的[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]，附近还有[[派勒特岩|派勒特岩]]（{{lang|en|Pilot Rock}}）、灰熊峰（{{lang|en|Grizzly Peak}}）和鲍尔迪（{{lang|en|Baldy}}）三座高山，都位于[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[杰克逊县_(俄勒冈州)|杰克逊县]]境内<ref name="City of Ashland-2006">{{cite web | last1 = City of Ashland | last2 = National Park Service | last3 = Ashland Woodlands and Trails Association | first4 = David R. | last4 = Lewis | url = http://www.ashland.or.us/Page.asp?NavID=9063#_Toc125530101 | title = Ashland Trails Master Plan: Appendix C: Geology | publisher = City of Ashland | date = 2006-02-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070824171332/http://www.ashland.or.us/Page.asp?NavID=9063#_Toc125530101 | archivedate = 2007-08-24 | accessdate = 2007-08-24 }}</ref><ref name="Bernstein-2001">{{cite book | title = Hiking Oregon's Southern Cascades and Siskiyous | first = Art | last = Bernstein | year = 2001 | publisher = Globe Pequot Press | location = Guilford, Connecticut | isbn = 978-1-56044-898-3 | oclc = 47292698 | chapterurl = http://books.google.com/books?id=H3dPI-DAO84C&pg=PA219 | chapter = Roxy Ann Peak | pages = 219–221}}</ref>。乐声安峰是由多个不同的地质层组成，其中年代最久远的是在3500到5000万前年形成的基底，包括[[沉积岩|沉积]][[砂岩|砂岩]]、[[页岩|页岩]]和[[砾岩|砾岩]]。山峰的其余部分主要是由已有3000到3500万年历史的火山[[玄武岩|玄武岩]]、[[角砾岩|角砾岩]]和[[集块岩|集块岩]]组成，人称乐声地层<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|10}}<ref name="LaLande-1983">{{cite book | title = A Historical Overview of Roxy Ann Peak and Prescott Park | first = Jeff | last = LaLande | date = 1983-01 | location = Medford, Oregon | oclc = 30562815}}</ref><ref name="Wiley-Smith-1993">{{cite book | first1 = Thomas J. | last1 = Wiley | first2 = James G. | last2 = Smith | title = Preliminary Geologic Map of the Medford East, Medford West, Eagle Point, and Sams Valley Quadrangles, Jackson County, Oregon | type = Map | publisher = Oregon Department of Geology and Mineral Industries | year = 1993 | oclc = 31263986}}</ref>，其中有整个[[喀斯喀特山脉|喀斯喀特山脉]]最古老的一些岩石<ref name="Quinn-1998">{{cite news |title=Colossal quake will come |last=Quinn |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113075134/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19981204%2FNEWS%2F312049981 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/19981204/NEWS/312049981 |first=Beth |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |date=1998-12-04 |accessdate=2014-07-31 |archivedate=2013-11-13 }}</ref>。峰顶由相对更耐侵蚀的玄武[[岩脉|岩脉]]构成，经[[钾氩定年法|钾氩定年法]]测定其形成年代约在3082万（±200万）年前<ref name="Wiley-Smith-1993" />，这种构成很可能是山顶成为类似圆锥形并与周围拉开高度差的重要原因<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|10}}<ref name="LaLande-1983" />。乐声安峰的大部分下部山坡由1.2到1.5米厚的致密[[黏土|黏土]]覆盖<ref name="Young-2008">{{cite web | accessdate = 2014-07-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140726023018/http://www.ci.medford.or.us/Files/Prescott%20Park%20Management%20Plan.PDF | url = http://www.ci.medford.or.us/Files/Prescott%20Park%20Management%20Plan.PDF | format = PDF | title = 2008 Prescott Park Master Plan | first = Pete | last = Young | date = 2008-04-15 | publisher = City of Medford Parks Commission | archivedate = 2014-07-26 }}</ref>{{rp|10}}<ref name="City of Medford-2008">{{cite web | page = 84 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131113075040/http://www.ci.medford.or.us/files/2008%20revised%20plan.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ci.medford.or.us/files/2008%20revised%20plan.pdf | format = PDF | title = City of Medford Pre-Disaster Mitigation Plan | publisher = City of Medford | date = 2008-12 | accessdate = 2014-07-31 | archivedate = 2013-11-13 }}</ref><ref name="Medford Planning Department-2011">{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-03-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140317003630/https://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Environmental%20Element%20October%202011.pdf | url = http://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Environmental%20Element%20October%202011.pdf | format = PDF | title = City of Medford Comprehensive Plan: Environmental Element | author = Medford Planning Department | publisher = City of Medford | date = 2011-10-06 | accessdate = 2014-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>{{rp|50}}。由于黏土的[[剪切强度|剪切强度]]低，土壤很容易出现[[下坡蠕变|蠕变]]、[[泥流|泥流]]和[[山崩|山体滑坡]]。这些沉积岩的最上方有多个已划分好的大规模房产开放区，其中部分土层的厚道达到6.1米<ref name="City of Medford-2008" /><ref name="Medford Planning Department-2011" />{{rp|50}}。

乐声安峰的海拔高度为1090米，[[地形突起度|相对高度]]230米<ref name="NGS-1991">{{cite web | url = http://www.ngs.noaa.gov/cgi-bin/ds_mark.prl?PidBox=NZ1108 | title = Roxy Ann | publisher = NGS data sheet. U.S. National Geodetic Survey | accessdate = 2014-07-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140829081747/http://www.ngs.noaa.gov/cgi-bin/ds_mark.prl?PidBox=NZ1108 | archivedate = 2014-08-29 }}</ref>{{#tag:ref|[[地形突起度|相对高度]]是通过将顶峰的1929年海平面数据1089米<ref name="NGS-1991" />减去其周围不包围更高山峰的最低等高线高度859.5米所得<ref name="TopoQuest">{{cite map | cartography = United States Geological Survey | title = United States Geological Survey Topographic Map: Rio Canyon quadrangle | accessdate = 2014-07-31 | publisher = TopoQuest | archivedate = 2014-07-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140731083150/http://www.topoquest.com/map.php?lat=42.32604&lon=-122.74792&datum=nad83&zoom=2&map=auto&coord=d&mode=zoomin&size=l | url = http://www.topoquest.com/map.php?lat=42.32604&lon=-122.74792&datum=nad83&zoom=2&map=auto&coord=d&mode=zoomin&size=l }}</ref>。|group="注"}}，比周围环绕的罗格谷要高670米<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|8-9}}。独特的圆形峰顶、山峰的位置和高度令其与周围景观形成明显对比，向北约25公里外的[[黑幕湾_(俄勒冈州)|黑幕湾]]（{{lang|en|Shady Cove}}）、向南远至约38公里外的[[锡斯基尤峰|锡斯基尤峰]]（{{lang|en|Siskiyou Summit}}）都能清晰地看到乐声安峰<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|5}}<ref name="Medford Planning Department">{{cite web | url = http://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Public%20Facilities%20Element.pdf | format = PDF | title = City of Medford Comprehensive Plan: Public Facilities Element | author = Medford Planning Department | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140731160949/http://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Public%20Facilities%20Element.pdf | archivedate = 2014-07-31 | accessdate = 2014-08-01 }}</ref>{{rp|73}}。

== 历史 ==
=== 早年历史 ===
人类从8000到10000年前就开始在乐声安峰附近生活<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|8-9}}<ref name="City of Medford-2006">{{cite web | publisher = City of Medford | accessdate = 2014-08-01 | url = http://www.ci.medford.or.us/Files/Prescott%20Brochure.pdf | format = PDF | title = Prescott Park | date = 2006-12-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120208172117/http://www.ci.medford.or.us/Files/Prescott%20Brochure.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-02-08 }}</ref>。最早的居民属于半[[游牧民族|游牧民族]]，他们很有可能是通过食用[[鳞茎|鳞茎]]及诸如[[乳齿象|乳齿象]]和[[長角野牛|長角野牛]]之类大型[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]维持生存<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|8-9}}<ref name="LaLande-1983" />。过去的1000年里，这片地区成为[[美洲原住民|美洲原住民]]部落拉特加瓦人的定居点，他们把乐声安峰称为“{{sans-serif|Al-wiya}}”（音似“阿瓦雅”）<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|8-9}}<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="Fattig-1998">{{cite news |title=Bits of lost Takelma language preserved |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |last=Fattig |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801011520/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19980816%2FNEWS%2F308169999 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/19980816/NEWS/308169999 |first=Paul |date=1998-08-16 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Miller-2007">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120207150830/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20070923%2FNEWS%2F709230322%2F-1%2FNEWS |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20070923/NEWS/709230322/-1/NEWS |title=A view of Roxy Ann Peak |last=Miller |first=Bill |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |date=2007-09-23 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2012-02-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Gray-1987">{{cite web | url = http://soda.sou.edu/awdata/021104a1.pdf | format = PDF | title = The Takelma and Their Athapascan Neighbors | first = Dennis J. | last = Gray | publisher = Southern Oregon University | year = 1987 | accessdate = 2014-08-01 | page = 75 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131205043528/http://soda.sou.edu/awdata/021104a1.pdf | archivedate = 2013-12-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。他们可能有利用这座山获取[[栓皮栎|栓皮栎]]、捕猎黑尾鹿和小鸟，这里至今仍然有许多这类动物生活<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="Fattig-1998" /><ref name="Miller-2007" />。

1827年2月14日，[[彼得·谢讷·奥格登|彼得·谢讷·奥格登]]（{{lang|en|Peter Skene Ogden}}）带领一队[[皮草贸易|毛皮捕手]]向北穿越罗格谷，成为首批造访这一地区的欧裔美国人<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|8-9}}<ref name="City of Medford-2006" />，第一批不是[[原住民|原住民]]的定居者则要到数十年后才前来此地。人口的突然增多导致外来者和拉特加瓦人发生冲突，最终在1855到1856年引发了罗格河战争。这场战争结束后，剩下的拉特加瓦人被迫向北迁居数百英里，到达如今俄勒冈州[[林肯县_(俄勒冈州)|林肯县]]境内的[[印第安保留地|保留地]]生活<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|8-9}}<ref name="LaLande-1983" />。

早期定居者以[[阿朗佐·A·斯金纳|阿朗佐·A·斯金纳]]（{{lang|en|Alonzo A. Skinner}}）之名把这座山峰命名成斯金纳峰，他是1851到1853年间罗格谷的印第安事务代理<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|8-9}}<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="Miller-2007" /><ref name="Since You Asked-2002">{{cite news |title=Now then, Jennings, here it is |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801014114/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20020928%2FBIZ%2F309289993 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20020928/BIZ/309289993 |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |author=Since You Asked |date=2002-09-28 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Since You Asked-2006">{{cite news |title=Roxy Ann is named for pioneer woman |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20060123/BIZ/301239992 |author=Since You Asked |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801014234/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20060123%2FBIZ%2F301239992 |date=2006-01-23 |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |accessdate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2014-08-01 }}</ref>。山峰如今使用的名称源于乐声·安·博文（{{lang|en|Roxy Ann Bowen}}），她是这里最早的定居者之一。1853年，乐声·安·博文和丈夫约翰·博文（{{lang|en|John Bowen}}），以及斯蒂芬·泰勒（{{lang|en|Stephen Taylor}}）和玛丽·泰勒（{{lang|en|Mary Taylor}}）两对夫妇宣布拥有几乎整座山峰的土地所有权，到了19世纪50年代末，这座山开始以乐声安峰之名为人所知<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|8-9}}<ref name="City of Medford-2006" /><ref name="Miller-2007" /><ref name="Since You Asked-2002" /><ref name="Since You Asked-2006" />。

1883年11月，[[俄勒冈和加利福尼亚铁路|俄勒冈和加利福尼亚铁路]]绕过杰克逊县城市[[杰克逊维尔_(俄勒冈州)|杰克逊维尔]]（{{lang|en|Jacksonville}}），从罗格谷中心穿过。铁路公司还在[[森特勒尔波因特_(俄勒冈州)|森特勒尔波因特]]（{{lang|en|Central Point}}）和[[菲尼克斯_(俄勒冈州)|菲尼克斯]]（{{lang|en|Phoenix}}）之间的中途位置建立了一个[[铁路车站|火车站]]，并绘制了其周围82个[[城市街区|城市街区]]的地图。同年12月，这一城址获名梅德福（{{lang|en|Medford}}）<ref name="Southern Oregon History, Revised-2012">{{cite web | url = http://id.mind.net/~truwe/tina/medford1883.html | title = Medford News: 1883 | date = 2012-07-22 | publisher = Southern Oregon History, Revised | accessdate = 2014-08-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120220092240/http://id.mind.net/~truwe/tina/medford1883.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-02-20 }}</ref>。1884年，镇上居民在乐声安峰的山顶用38声礼炮庆祝第一个[[美国独立日|国庆节]]，每一响代表[[美国州份依加入联邦顺序排列列表|美国的一个州]]<ref name="Miller-2007" /><ref name="Miller-2009">{{cite news |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20090705/NEWS/307059981 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801021038/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20090705%2FNEWS%2F307059981 |title=How Medford celebrated the first big blast |last=Miller |first=Bill |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |date=2009-07-05 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2014-08-01 }}</ref>。梅德福的发展十分迅速，于1885年2月24日[[市法团|注册成市]]<ref name=Oregon>{{cite book | author = Oregon Legislative Assembly | title = The Laws of Oregon | year = 1891 | publisher = Baker, Frank C. | location = Salem, Oregon | page = 986 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=Yr2wAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA986 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170505134156/https://books.google.com/books?id=Yr2wAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA986 | archivedate = 2017-05-05 | access-date = 2014-08-01 }}</ref>。

从20世纪初开始，乐声安峰的山脚主要成为[[梨|梨]]树种植地和[[褐煤|褐煤]]开采地。其中采矿业在[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]爆发后中止，许多果园都在[[大萧条|大萧条]]期间废弃，但仍然有一部分留存至今<ref name="LaLande-1983" />。

=== 普雷斯科特公园 ===
[[File:Prescott_Park_Plaque.jpg|thumb]]
1929年，[[国际狮子会|国际狮子会]]购买了山上两块很大的土地，并于次年将其中80.9公顷立契过户给梅德福用于建设康乐休闲场所<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|5}}<ref name="Medford Planning Department" />{{rp|73}}<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="City of Medford-2012">{{cite web | accessdate = 2014-08-01 | year = 2012 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140801022312/http://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Regional%20Plan%20Element.pdf | url = http://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Regional%20Plan%20Element.pdf | format = PDF | title = City of Medford Comprehensive Plan: Regional Plan Element | publisher = City of Medford | archivedate = 2014-08-01 }}</ref>{{rp|47}}<ref name="Since You Asked-2009">{{cite news |title=Prescott Park has its origins in 1929 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306001218/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20090101%2FNEWS%2F901010331%2F-1%2Frss01 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20090101/NEWS/901010331/-1/rss01 |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |author=Since You Asked |date=2009-01-01 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2012-03-06 }}</ref>。1931年，该市再通过《康乐和公共目的法案》（{{lang|en|Recreation and Public Purposes Act}}）收购了607公顷土地<ref name="City of Medford-2012" />{{rp|47}}<ref name="City of Medford-2006" />，1933年又收购了16公顷<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|5}}<ref name="Medford Planning Department" />{{rp|73}}。1937年，建成的公园命名为普雷斯科特公园，来向狮子会领导人、梅福德警察乔治·{{lang|en|J}}·普雷斯科特（{{lang|en|George J. Prescott}}）致敬，他于1933年3月16日因工殉职<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="Briskley-2003">{{cite news |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20030316/BIZ/303169995 |title=Rededication ceremony honors Medford's first traffic officer who was shot and killed |last=Briskley |first=Jill |work=Mail Tribune |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801023204/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20030316%2FBIZ%2F303169995 |location=Medford, Oregon |date=2003-03-16 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Officer Down Memorial Page">{{cite web | archivedate = 2007-08-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070803001135/http://odmp.org/officer/10829-constable-george-j.-prescott | url = http://www.odmp.org/officer/10829-constable-george-j.-prescott | title = Constable George J. Prescott | publisher = Officer Down Memorial Page | accessdate = 2007-08-03 }}</ref>。

从1933年开始，[[平民保育团|平民保育团]]对普雷斯科特公园进行了第一轮改善，其中包括修建29公里长的步道和以及通向公园、宽4.9米的乐声安路，还建立了多个野餐地和观景处，并且挖出了几条排水沟<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="City of Medford-2012" />{{rp|47}}<ref name="City of Medford-2006" /><ref name="Dunn-1993">{{cite book | title = Land in Common | editor-first = Joy B. | editor-last = Dunn | year = 1993 | publisher = Southern Oregon Historical Society | location = Medford, Oregon | isbn = 978-0-943388-11-3 | oclc = 29427009 | page = 98}}</ref>。[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]爆发后不久，平民保育团停止了工作。由于市政预算不足，公园的维护工作只能中止，[[配给|汽油配给]]也导致游客数量明显下降。到了1956年，平民保育团所做的改善工作已经遭受了11万美元的损失<ref name="LaLande-1983" />。这种年久失修的趋势接下来又持续了几十年<ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="Briskley-2003" />。

时间进入20世纪90年代末时，公园中破坏、乱扔垃圾的行为以及因[[越野|越野]]兴起造成的野火都出现激增<ref name="Briskley-2003" /><ref name="Smith-2000">{{cite news |last=Smith |first=Jessica |date=2000-07-22 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20000722/NEWS/307229999 |title=Police, neighbors work together to curtail damage to Prescott Park |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801030129/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20000722%2FNEWS%2F307229999 |archivedate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，乐声安路因缺乏维护而变得几乎无法通行。由于公园位置偏远，梅德福的警员不得不花费大量时间到山上巡逻。为了缓解这些问题，梅德福市于1998年对乐声安路进行了彻底整修<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|14-15}}，并于两年后在靠近公园入口处安装了两扇大门<ref name="Briskley-2003" /><ref name="Smith-2000" />。到了2006年，人为破坏已经减少了70%<ref name="City of Medford-2006" />。

普雷斯科特公园占地面积为704.2公顷<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|1}}<ref name="City of Medford-2012" />{{rp|8}}<ref name="Danielsson-Danielsson-2003">{{cite book | title = A Bark in the Park | first1 = Matt | last1 = Danielsson | first2 = Krissi | last2 = Danielsson | year = 2003 | publisher = Cruden Bay Books | location = Montchanin, Delaware | isbn = 978-0-9744083-1-6 | oclc = 56528636 | page = 32–33 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=hpTz2f2eDU0C&lpg=PA27&pg=PA32 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170505095830/https://books.google.com/books?id=hpTz2f2eDU0C&lpg=PA27&pg=PA32 | archivedate = 2017-05-05 | access-date = 2014-08-01 }}</ref>，是梅福德最大的公园，覆盖了乐声安峰的山顶和大部分上山坡。并且面积还达到该市其它公园总和的2.5倍<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|1}}<ref name="Lemon-2012">{{cite news |title=Challenge on the peak |accessdate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801035128/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20120618%2FOREGONHEALTHYLIVING%2F206180301 |date=2012-06-18 |work=Mail Tribune |last=Lemon |archivedate=2014-08-01 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20120618/OREGONHEALTHYLIVING/206180301 |first=Sarah |location=Medford, Oregon }}</ref>。

=== 21世纪 ===
[[File:Roxy_Ann_Tower.jpg|thumb]]
普雷斯科特公园和乐声安峰的上山坡基本上保持在相对未经人类开发利用的状态，所处位置在梅德福市区范围和[[城市增长边界|城市增长边界]]以外<ref name="Medford Planning Department" />{{rp|73}}<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|14-15}}<ref name="City of Medford-2012" />{{rp|8}}。2007年，峰顶建成一座高54.9米的无线电发射塔，取代了原有的3到4个24米高的塔<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|14-15}}<ref name=Miller-2006>{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-08-01 | url = http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20061231/NEWS/312319996 | title = Tower will improve emergency services | last = Miller | first = Bill | work = Mail Tribune | location = Medford, Oregon | date = 2006-12-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140801030158/http://www.mailtribune.com/section/?template=ajaxWeather | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-08-01 }}</ref>。乐声安峰和附近的鲍尔迪是罗格谷仅有的两个主要[[发射机站|发射机站]]所在地<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|14-15}}。

山峰南麓的住宅开发已连续多年呈上升趋势<ref name="Medford Planning Department-2011" />{{rp|7-8}}<ref name="Medford Planning Department-2013" />{{rp|9-10}}，其中又以单户住宅为主<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|14-15}}。建设的成本也出现明显上升，这其中部分是因为2003年通过的第3375号俄勒冈州众议院法案，其中要求任何在欠稳定土壤上施工、并且坡度大于20%的新建筑项目需要经过更多的审批流程，并且监管工作也会增强。法案中把新建[[基础|地基]]的成本提高了一倍，达到2万到3万美元，对于已有建筑的改造成本则达到了10万美元<ref name="Mann-2003">{{cite news |location=Medford, Oregon |accessdate=2014-08-01 |title=Foundation against sliding |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20031206/BIZ/312069997 |date=2003-12-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801041058/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20031206%2FBIZ%2F312069997 |archivedate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes |last=Mann |first=Damian |work=Mail Tribune }}</ref>。

乐声安峰的南部山麓也是乐声安酒庄的所在地，这是一间建于2002年的罗格谷葡萄酒庄<ref name="RoxyAnn Winery">{{cite web |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/99999999/LIFE07/70416012 |publisher=''Mail Tribune'' |title=RoxyAnn Winery |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2013-09-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130902004003/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F99999999%2FLIFE07%2F70416012 }}</ref>。山的另一边建有干溪填埋场，是南俄勒冈第一个生物反应器填埋场，源于2006年一个通过收集甲烷来发电的项目<ref name="Medford Planning Department" />{{rp|108}}<ref name="Medford Planning Department-2013">{{cite web | url = http://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Conclusions%20Goals%20etc%209_19_13.pdf | format = PDF | title = City of Medford Comprehensive Plan: Conclusions, Goals, Policies, and Implementation Strategies | author = Medford Planning Department | publisher = City of Medford | date = 2013-03-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140801041224/http://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Conclusions%20Goals%20etc%209_19_13.pdf | archivedate = 2014-08-01 | accessdate = 2014-08-01 }}</ref>{{rp|62}}<ref name="Darling-2006">{{cite news |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |title=Power Garbage |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801040215/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20060921%2FNEWS%2F309219999 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20060921/NEWS/309219999 |last=Darling |first=John |date=2006-09-21 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2009年9月21日，乐声安峰的西山峰爆发野火，烧毁的面积约有256公顷<ref name="Mann-2010">{{cite news |title=Medford fire area shows signs of life |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20100920/NEWS/9200317 |date=2010-09-20 |last=Mann |first=Damian |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801042534/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20100920%2FNEWS%2F9200317 |archivedate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-08-01 }}</ref><ref name="Stiles-2009">{{cite news |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20090922/NEWS07/909229997 |archivedate=2012-09-16 |title=Crews have line around 633-acre Medford fire |last=Stiles |first=Greg |work=Mail Tribune |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120916130603/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20090922%2FNEWS07%2F909229997 |location=Medford, Oregon |date=2009-09-22 |accessdate=2014-08-01 }}</ref><ref name="Mail Tribune, Grass fire-2009">{{cite news |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20090921/NEWS07/909219991 |date=2009-09-21 |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |title=Grass fire on Roxy Ann threatens Medford homes; roads closed |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2012-09-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120916130122/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20090921%2FNEWS07%2F909219991 }}</ref>。火灾导致2.5万居民家中[[停电|停电]]，超过100户家庭被迫撤离<ref name="Mail Tribune, Crews-2009">{{cite news |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20090921/NEWS07/909210337/0/NEWSMAP |date=2009-09-21 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |title=Crews protect evacuated houses, some residents likely to return home soon |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |archivedate=2012-09-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120916130313/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20090921%2FNEWS07%2F909210337%2F0%2FNEWSMAP }}</ref><ref name="Achen-2009">{{cite news |date=2009-09-22 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20090922/NEWS/909220318 |title=Medford fire chars 600 acres |last=Achen |first=Paris |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |archivedate=2012-09-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120916130345/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20090922%2FNEWS%2F909220318 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Burke-2009">{{cite news |archivedate=2012-09-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120916130227/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20090921%2FNEWS07%2F909219988 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20090921/NEWS07/909219988 |title=Medford fire leaves 25,000 without power, snarls traffic |last=Burke |first=Anita |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |date=2009-09-21 |accessdate=2014-08-01 }}</ref>，扑灭这场大火所花费的成本超过130万美元，不过没有建筑物在这期间受损<ref name="Mann-2010" /><ref name="Stiles-2009" />。

== 动植物 ==
[[File:Roxy_Ann_Peak_Madrone.JPG|thumb]]
由于海拔高度范围大，并且地处[[喀斯喀特生态区|喀斯喀特]]、[[克拉马斯生态区|克拉马斯]]和[[东喀斯喀特生态区|东喀斯喀特]]三个生态区之间，乐声安峰拥有高度的[[生物多样性|生物多样性]]<ref name="The Nature Conservancy-1975">{{cite web | url = http://ir.library.oregonstate.edu/xmlui/bitstream/handle/1957/22011/NaturalAreaIdentificationProtection.pdf?sequence=1 | format = PDF | title = Natural Area Identification and Protection | year = 1975 | author = The Nature Conservancy | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140801044735/http://ir.library.oregonstate.edu/xmlui/bitstream/handle/1957/22011/NaturalAreaIdentificationProtection.pdf?sequence=1 | publisher = Oregon State University | accessdate = 2014-08-01 | page = 135 | archivedate = 2014-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。山的下山坡主要生长有灌木丛、橡树稀树草原和开阔[[草原|草原]]<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|11-12}}<ref name="The Nature Conservancy-1975" />，也有零散的[[加州黑橡树|加州黑橡树]]、[[俄勒冈白橡树|俄勒冈白橡树]]和[[太平洋乔鹃木|太平洋乔鹃木]]<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|11-12}}<ref name="The Nature Conservancy-1975" /><ref name="Martin-2001">{{cite news |accessdate=2014-08-01 |title=Shade Trees vs Power Lines |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801045525/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20011103%2FNEWS%2F311039994 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20011103/NEWS/311039994 |date=2001-11-14 |last=Martin |first=Melissa |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |archivedate=2014-08-01 }}</ref>，还有像[[白桦叶山桃木|白桦叶山桃木]]、[[粘白叶熊果树|粘白叶熊果树]]、[[三裂单花木|羚羊蔷薇科]]和[[太平洋毒橡树|太平洋毒橡树]]之类的[[硬叶林|硬叶]]灌木林<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|11-12}}<ref name="The Nature Conservancy-1975" /><ref name="Freeman-2008">{{cite news |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20081002/LIFE/810020301 |title=Hidden 'danger' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306001250/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20081002%2FLIFE%2F810020301 |last=Freeman |first=Mark |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |date=2008-10-02 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2012-03-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。常见的草类包括[[粉绿披碱草|蓝羊草]]和[[溚草|溚草]]。野花则有[[毛茛属|南俄勒冈毛茛]]、[[蓍|常见蓍草]]和[[托尔米蝴蝶百合|托尔米星形郁金星]]<ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|11-12}}。海拔更高的山坡上开始向混合型针叶林过渡，其中又以[[花旗松|花旗松]]、[[西黄松|西黄松]]、[[北美翠柏|拟肖楠属]]、[[美国西部圆柏|西部圆柏]]和太平洋玛都那树为主<ref name="The Nature Conservancy-1975" /><ref name="Browning-1975">{{cite journal | url = http://soda.sou.edu/awdata/030923d1.pdf | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | title = The Distribution and Occurrence of the Birds of Jackson County, Oregon | last = Browning | first = M. Ralph | publisher = United States Fish and Wildlife Service | year = 1975 | work = North American Fauna, Number 70 | accessdate = 2008-02-20 | page = 19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110720045251/http://soda.sou.edu/awdata/030923d1.pdf | archivedate = 2011-07-20 | journal =  }}</ref><ref name="Rakestraw-2007">{{cite book | title = Birding Oregon | last = Rakestraw | first = John | year = 2007 | publisher = Globe Pequot Press | location = Guilford, Connecticut | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=V741Dgud3RcC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA100 | isbn = 978-0-7627-3913-4 | oclc = 65165451 | page = 100 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140707141444/http://books.google.com/books?id=V741Dgud3RcC | archivedate = 2014-07-07 }}</ref><ref name="Kettler-2003">{{cite news |title=Under bright skies or lost in fog, Prescott Park enchants |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20030228/NEWS/302289985 |date=2003-02-28 |last=Kettler |first=Bill |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |accessdate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801052238/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20030228%2FNEWS%2F302289985 |archivedate=2014-08-01 }}</ref>。树林的下木层则由[[小花毛核木|红雪果]]、[[绿叶熊果属|绿叶熊果属]]、粘白叶熊果树、[[鹿刷尾草|鹿刷尾草]]和太平洋毒橡树等灌木组成，还有像[[匍枝雪果|匍枝雪果]]和[[爱达荷州高羊茅|爱达荷州高羊茅]]之类的[[草本植物|草本植物]]<ref name="The Nature Conservancy-1975" />。

山上生活有多种[[鸟类|鸟类]]，其中包括生活在下山坡的[[蓝灰蚋鹩|蓝灰蚋鹩]]、[[琉璃彩鵐|琉璃彩鵐]]、[[橡树山雀|橡树山雀]]、[[橡树啄木鸟|橡树啄木鸟]]和[[珠颈翎鹑|珠颈翎鹑]]，以及生活在上山坡的[[高山鹑|高山鹑]]、[[北美白眉山雀|北美白眉山雀]]和[[红胸鳾|红胸鳾]]<ref name="Browning-1975" /><ref name="Rakestraw-2007" />。像[[库柏鹰|库柏鹰]]、[[金雕|金雕]]、[[白头海鵰|白头海鵰]]和[[草原隼|草原隼]]之类的[[野生火鸡|野生火鸡]]及[[猛禽|猛禽]]也很常见<ref name="Briskley-2003" /><ref name="Browning-1975" />。有少量物种会[[鸟类迁徙|迁徙]]到山上过冬，如[[红玉冠戴菊鸟|红玉冠戴菊鸟]]、[[黄腰白喉林莺|黄腰白喉林莺]]和[[金冠带鹀|金冠带鹀]]<ref name="Browning-1975" /><ref name="Rakestraw-2007" />。生活在山上的哺乳动物有[[黑尾鹿|黑尾鹿]]、[[美洲狮|美洲狮]]、[[短尾猫|短尾猫]]、[[臭鼬科|臭鼬]]、[[浣熊|浣熊]]、[[郊狼|郊狼]]、[[熊科|熊]]、[[鼬属|鼬]]和[[松鼠|松鼠]]<ref name="City of Medford-2006" /><ref name="Briskley-2003" /><ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|11-12}}。有一大群[[罗斯福马鹿|罗斯福马鹿]]经常在山的西部山麓出没，其数量在2000年代中期一度膨胀到超过100头，造成了许多交通问题，还对当地梨园构成严重破坏，为此俄勒冈州鱼类和野生动物部将许多鹿迁至别处，到2009年时还剩下约40头<ref name=Freeman-2009>{{cite news |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20090113/NEWS/901130310 |title=Forbidden fruit solves elk problem |last=Freeman |first=Mark |work=Mail Tribune |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801061522/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20090113%2FNEWS%2F901130310 |location=Medford, Oregon |date=2009-01-13 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archivedate=2014-08-01 }}</ref>。山上常见的其它野生动物包括[[西部响尾蛇|西部响尾蛇]]和[[太平洋硬蜱|西部黑足蜱]]<ref name="City of Medford-2006" />。

== 康乐休闲 ==
[[File:View_East_from_Roxy_Ann_Peak.jpg|thumb]]
乐声安峰和普雷斯科特公园是梅德福最重要的视域、游憩和休闲所在<ref name="Medford Planning Department-2011" />{{rp|7-8}}<ref name="Medford Planning Department-2013" />{{rp|9-10}}<ref name="Medford Planning Department" />{{rp|108}}。山上的热门休闲活动包括野餐、[[远足|远足]]和[[山地自行车|山地自行车]]，普雷斯科特公园还有一段长6公里的专用道可以练习[[马术|马术]]，其斜度范围从适中到陡峭不等<ref name="City of Medford-2006" /><ref name="Danielsson-Danielsson-2003" /><ref name="Mann-2013">{{cite news |title=Roxy Ann Peak may get larger bike network |archivedate=2014-08-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801063132/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20130821%2FNEWS%2F308210311 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20130821/NEWS/308210311 |date=2013-08-21 |last=Mann |first=Damian |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |accessdate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2013年8月，梅德福市和[[国际山地自行车协会|国际山地自行车协会]]一起公布了概念性的方案，详细说明公园步道系统未来的改善方面。这一方案计划在整个园区新建48公里的多用途步道，对已有步道及其指示牌作出改善，在山的西面增加新登山口，这些工作的预计成本约在36到72万美元之间<ref name="Mann-2013" /><ref name=IMBA-2013>{{cite report | url = http://rvmba.org/news/prescott-park-conceptual-trail-plan/ | archivedate = 2013-10-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131016230716/http://rvmba.org/news/prescott-park-conceptual-trail-plan/ | title = Prescott Park Conceptual Trail Plan | date = 2013-08 | author = International Mountain Bicycling Association | publisher = City of Medford | accessdate = 2014-08-01 | pages = 10–13 }}</ref>。如果获得批准，第一阶段的建设工作将从2015年启动<ref name="Mann-2013" />。

2012年4月，总部位于[[华盛顿县_(俄勒冈州)|华盛顿县]][[泰格德_(俄勒冈州)|泰格德]]（{{lang|en|Tigard}}）的一家公司在普雷斯科特公园开设了[[绳索课程|挑战课程]]，其中包括15种不同项目，8个地面项目和7个空中项目，每一个都由绳索、金属线、平台、爬梯和秋千组合而成，高度范围在距地面0.6米到12米之间。<ref name="Lemon-2012" /><ref name="City of Medford-Synergo-2013">{{cite web | publisher = City of Medford | date = 2013-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140718005949/http://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Prescott%20Park%20Challenge%20Course%20March%202013.pdf | archivedate = 2014-07-18 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ci.medford.or.us/SIB/files/Prescott%20Park%20Challenge%20Course%20March%202013.pdf | format = PDF | title = Prescott Park Challenge Course | author1 = City of Medford | author2 = Synergo }}</ref>

游客可以通过位于山南面的乐声安路前往乐声安峰和普雷斯科特公园。路上有两道门，第一道位于山基附近，根据规定时间开放，第二道在第一道门后约1600米，位于公园边界，所有未经许可的车辆不得入内<ref name="City of Medford-2006" /><ref name="Kettler-2001">{{cite news |title=Prescott Park gets new gate |accessdate=2014-08-01 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20010403/NEWS/304039995 |last=Kettler |first=Bill |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801075558/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20010403%2FNEWS%2F304039995 |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |date=2001-04-03 |archivedate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Landers-2003">{{cite news |title=Some Hillcrest Road residents want to keep off |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801075727/http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20030329%2FBIZ%2F303299997 |url=http://www.mailtribune.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20030329/BIZ/303299997 |date=2003-03-29 |last=Landers |first=Meg |work=Mail Tribune |location=Medford, Oregon |accessdate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2014-08-01 }}</ref>。经过第二座门约1600米后，道路会分成围绕山顶的环路，全长4.3公里，环路北侧有可以登上山顶的塔路<ref name="City of Medford-2006" />。山上可以欣赏周围的广阔景观，包括罗格谷、阿什兰山、[[麦克拉克林峰|麦克拉克林峰]]、派勒特罗克、[[火山口湖_(美国)|火山口湖]]周边，甚至向北110公里外的[[锡尔森山|锡尔森山]]（{{lang|en|Mount Thielsen}}）和向南120公里外的[[沙斯塔山|沙斯塔山]]<ref name="Bernstein-2001" /><ref name="LaLande-1983" /><ref name="Danielsson-Danielsson-2003" /><ref name="Young-2008" />{{rp|11-12}}。

